Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.45,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,Don't go, Kugisaki{**-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:15.95,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,Remember what Nanami{**-san} said?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:19.34,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,The whole reason they kept quiet about Ieiri{**-san}{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.95,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,...was to prevent me from doing something reckless like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.38,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That's probably why these people were late getting here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.46,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:35.59,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I can't be the only one going back when those two are out there fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.97,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.92,Default,Nitta,0,0,0,,Kugisaki{**-san}!
Comment: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:01.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:43.10,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I should have asked Dagon to leave a few more humans for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.43,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Still, this is plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.56,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.45,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.67,Default,Mob,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.04,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.08,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.69,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's wary of both my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.62,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have heard the report from that 7:3 sorcerer, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.35,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm only a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.79,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can still alter my own shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.53,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't tweak transfigured humans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.40,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}or interfere with the souls of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.54,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}So thanks for wearing your nerves down all on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.20,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I already told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.17,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,that won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.04,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:54.08,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Sometimes you still have to try, despite knowing it's futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.77,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hairpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.58,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's jumping down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does this girl hope to achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.65,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Here's another!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.44,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hairpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.88,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}She used the nails that had fallen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.39,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:26.30,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,ever since I heard about your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I bet this one will work nicely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.14,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Resonance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.32,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.13,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.82,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:56.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itadori Yuji wasn't my only natural enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.48,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:05.59,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I just felt my cursed energy explode far away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.69,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,The pressure from your cursed energy is also lackluster,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:12.15,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,and you could have just taken hold of me earlier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.60,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:17.60,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,some kind of double who can't use its technique, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.71,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.95,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her technique's aftereffects are lingering a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.92,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still can't get my body to move like it should!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.67,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kugisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.21,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.58,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.40,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I caused everyone's efforts to end in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.90,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.89,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've let me believe that I'm not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.41,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.90,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.98,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.88,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that Resonance is working,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:25.09,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}it shouldn't fire off attacks as rapidly as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,This is where the real battle begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.42,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.31,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,I'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.81,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.31,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could ignore it and head straight for floor B5,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.23,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}but if I let that thing run free,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.06,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}it'll just cause more issues later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.91,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Underground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.79,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.98,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll exorcise it and keep heading down to floor B5!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.08,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}It split apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.42,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:17.60,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of them should have the fatal portion of its soul for me to crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.10,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,You fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.11,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit! I got tricked by its cursed energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.43,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are two Mahitos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:39.18,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had a double that was acting separately?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.86,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he's planning to merge it back in and heal himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.23,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Itadori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:05.72,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Run! Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.00,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hit you dead-on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.16,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.28,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.60,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:28.35,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't able to completely finish off the 7:3 sorcerer with just one touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.47,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.56,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Die, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:59.20,Default,Fumi's Father,0,0,0,,You're too naïve, Nobara{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.64,Default,Fumi's Father,0,0,0,,You have to make sure you crush their chance to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.33,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:11.34,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought everyone in my village was crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:16.30,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I was convinced I was the only sane one.
Comment: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:23.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.44,Default,Fumi's Mother,0,0,0,,You'll be using it until sixth grade, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:41.95,Default,Fumi's Mother,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:42.93,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.10,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that's what my mother said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.04,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I chose the blue backpack anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:53.32,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We moved to this village at the same time I was starting elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.45,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}My parents were worried about the inconveniences of the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:01.00,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I didn't like being separated from my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.49,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were nineteen students in the whole school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.66,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just one class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.23,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone had either a red or a black backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:14.40,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I liked both red and black,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:18.07,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but apparently everyone hated blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.24,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.14,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.12,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.16,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,let's trade backpacks, Fumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.87,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.20,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Let's trade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.63,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.79,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm number one in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.49,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hey! Kugisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.40,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.67,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Kugisaki! You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.66,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Shut up, old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:43.16,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:48.40,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}My backpack came back to me before the day was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.22,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I hate all backpacks in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.62,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:56.62,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that day, Nobara{**-chan} started coming over to my house a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:59.24,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and playing video games with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.27,Default,Father,0,0,0,,You've gotten better at aerials.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:07.01,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} hated the other villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.43,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,It's such a small village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,that it's harder to be strangers than friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:20.80,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought, "Isn't that a good thing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.84,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the old lady next door brought red rice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.44,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}to celebrate my first period several years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:32.56,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally understood the creepiness that Nobara{**-chan} was referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.11,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.44,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I found a secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.13,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes Nobara{**-chan} would say things you wouldn't expect from a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.39,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but then she'd suddenly say things like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.84,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,We're living here starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:59.24,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking back, those were probably things she picked up from someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.36,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like her mother, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.45,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.45,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan}'s so-called secret base was just someone else's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.37,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.80,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Oh, you really did come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.73,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Welcome. It's cold out, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.62,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl's name was Saori{**-chan},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.62,0:14:27.52,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she had moved into the village after I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:37.04,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We always visited her out of the blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.09,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she always welcomed us without a hint of displeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.84,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I think about it, Saori{**-chan} was always at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:49.23,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} changed after she met Saori{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:52.52,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Why, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.44,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,You sound like Matsuko{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.92,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi, let me practice braiding your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.92,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:03.40,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her speech grew softer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:08.01,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and it felt like she started to become more refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:12.08,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were both outsiders,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:15.59,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but everything was different between me and Saori{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.36,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}A little while after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:24.24,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}things at Saori{**-chan}'s house started to look strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.20,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was piled up trash, graffiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:31.05,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}snow that was clearly piled up in front of it by someone else, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:35.06,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}It made her nice house start to feel unsettling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.97,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not too much longer after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.68,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saori{**-chan} moved away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:54.92,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw her off together with Nobara{**-chan},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:16:01.44,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't remember what the weather was like or what anyone said at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:09.07,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only remember Nobara{**-chan} bawling with tears streaming down her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.57,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized she could cry, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:17.68,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the shock of that meant nothing else made it into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.56,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}In June of this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.45,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nobara{**-chan} was set to start going to high school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:41.66,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}She fought with her grandma over it, and that apparently caused some delays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.79,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm never coming back here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.98,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,So make sure you get out of this village at some point, too, Fumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:51.94,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:58.26,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The awful thought of, "So she won't cry for me," crossed my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.43,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and left me unable to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:05.43,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}We never spoke of Saori{**-chan} again after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.09,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.64,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Let's make sure all three of us are together when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.15,Default,Fumi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.24,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Saori, why don't you rest for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.95,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I can't. The proofs are due today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.46,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Or I guess yesterday at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.28,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,It's still today until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.98,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Ugh, I have a pimple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.92,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Shibuya's in trouble. Terrorism, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.85,0:18:36.44,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Senpai, were you ever hoping to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.59,Default,Coworker,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:44.32,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Well, I was just thinking it wasn't supposed to turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.38,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I moved out into the sticks during my second year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:49.45,Default,Senpai,0,0,0,,A parent's work transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:54.24,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,No, my mother was a crazy woman who was into organics and spiritualism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:56.39,Default,Senpai,0,0,0,,I think I get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.36,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,While I was there, I met these two girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:07.08,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,Seven years younger, I guess, and this one, Nobara{**-chan}, really took a liking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.68,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I was an only child,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.84,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,so I thought Nobara{**-chan} was just the cutest thing ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.01,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,and I forced myself to act like an older sister, hoping she'd like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.00,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I even served them tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.36,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,For first graders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.68,Default,Sempai,0,0,0,,That's kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.78,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I never did give them my contact info, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.44,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I was afraid of us slowly growing further apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:48.53,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,and she really cried her eyes out when I left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.90,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:55.94,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I wonder if she would be disappointed to see how I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.56,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I hope Nobara{**-chan}'s doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.97,Default,Saori,0,0,0,,I wonder where she is and what she's up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:17.72,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Everyone in the village was crazy."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}That notion was never true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.94,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the crazy ones have the louder voices,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.89,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}and make it seem like they're all there is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.32,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}so they can trample all over other people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:41.36,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Though I guess that wasn't entirely the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.40,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.52,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,I couldn't keep our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:20.58,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Itadori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:22.29,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Tell everyone for me:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:26.57,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Life wasn't so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.96,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Kugisaki?
Comment: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.09,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:25.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:28.01,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}When I first stepped off at Tokyo Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:32.36,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was a bit grossed out because the air smelled like I was standing behind a truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.80,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now it doesn't bother me at all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.87,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time, Right and Wrong, Part 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:39.55,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}I guess life's all about the dirt we pick up.
